>> PhonePanel (add to DashboardLayout — renders on EVERY page):
- Position: fixed bottom-4 right-4 (LTR) / bottom-4 left-4 (RTL)
- Uses useJsSip() from src/lib/hooks/useJsSip.ts (DO NOT rewrite)
- Uses useCallsStore from src/lib/store/calls.ts
- Idle: small collapsed button (Phone icon bg-brand-primary)
- Active call: expanded — contact name, count-up timer, Mute/Hold/End
- Incoming: IncomingCallToast via sonner

IncomingCallToast:
- Triggered by subscribeToCallEvents() on 'call.ringing'
- sonner toast.custom() with Answer (green) + Decline (red)
- On answer: useJsSip().answerCall(session)
- Screen pop: searchContacts(phoneNumber) → show contact name

ActiveCallBar (at top of main content when callsStore.activeCall !== null):
- Contact name, phone, elapsed timer (count-up 00:00)
- Mute/Hold/End mini-buttons
- On End: useJsSip().hangup() + endCall(sessionId)

>> Calling page layout: [220px call-list] | [flex-1 call-panel] | [240px dialpad]

Call-list sidebar:
- PSTN / WhatsApp tab switcher (border-b tabs)
- Active section: listActiveSessions() — name, green "Live" badge, timer
- Recent section: listCDR({ limit: 20 }) — name, Ended/Missed badge, duration

Call panel TopBar:
- Contact name + queue
- AgentStateSelector dropdown: Available/Busy/Break/Offline
  · setAgentState(agentId, state) from routing API
  · dot colors: Available=green, Busy=amber, Break=pink, Offline=gray

Incoming call banner (callsStore.incomingCalls.length > 0):
- bg-green-50 border-green-200 rounded-lg
- Initials avatar, name, number, queue
- Answer (green Phone) + Decline (red PhoneOff) buttons

Active call card (callsStore.activeCall !== null):
- Initials avatar, contact name, number, SLA tier badge
- Count-up timer (large, brand-primary)
- Controls: Mute | Hold | Transfer | Merge | DTMF | Record | End (red)
  · Mute: useJsSip().mute()/unmute(), highlights blue when muted
  · Hold: holdCall(sessionId) + useJsSip().hold()
  · Record: POST /api/recordings, button goes red
  · Transfer: modal with agent/queue select

DialPad (right panel):
- Number display + 3×4 key grid + Call button
- PSTN: useJsSip().makeCall(number)
- WhatsApp: createSession({ transport: 'whatsapp', to: number })
- Supervisor section (role === 'supervisor'|'admin'): Silent listen | Whisper | Barge
  · supervisorListen/Whisper/Barge from routing API

>> Wallboard (full-width, no secondary sidebar, refetchInterval: 5000):
TopBar: "Realtime wallboard" + pulsing green dot + queue filter select

KPI row (5 cards) from getQueueStats():
- Active calls (blue)
- Waiting (amber if > 5)
- Agents online/total (green)
- Handled today (neutral)
- Missed today (red if miss rate > 10%)

Queue breakdown (2-col grid) from listQueues():
- Name, avg wait, Waiting / Active / Agents / Handled counts

Agent states table from listAgents():
Columns: Agent | State pill | Current call | Duration | Handled today | Actions
- Available=green, Busy=amber, Break=pink, Offline=gray
- Listen/Whisper/Barge only on Busy rows
- Skeleton while loading

>> IVR Builder layout: [180px palette+flows] | [flex-1 canvas] | [200px properties]

Node palette (click-to-add for v1):
- Play message (blue) | DTMF menu (green) | Voice bot (amber) | Route to queue (teal)
- Condition (purple) | Collect input (pink) | Hangup (red)

Flows list below palette: listFlows() — click to load, "New flow" → createFlow()

IVRFlowCanvas:
- Light gray dotted-grid background (CSS radial-gradient)
- Nodes: absolute-positioned white cards — colored icon badge, title, description
- Port circles (top=in, bottom=out) for connections
- SVG overlay for connector lines between nodes
- Render saved flow from getFlow(flowId) in preset layout
- Click to select → sends to PropertiesPanel (border-brand-primary)

IVRPropertiesPanel (for selected node):
- Play message: label input, TTS text textarea
- DTMF menu: label, prompt, timeout (number), max retries, key→node mapping rows
- Route to queue: label, queue select, max wait, overflow destination
- Save: updateFlow(flowId, nodes)

TopBar: "Test flow" | "History" | "Publish" → publishFlow(flowId)

>> useCalls.ts:
export function useActiveSessions() {
  return useQuery({ queryKey: ['activeSessions'], queryFn: listActiveSessions, refetchInterval: 5000 })
}
export function useCDR(filters) {
  return useQuery({ queryKey: ['cdr', filters], queryFn: () => listCDR(filters) })
}

>> useAgentState.ts:
export function useAgents() {
  return useQuery({ queryKey: ['agents'], queryFn: listAgents, refetchInterval: 5000 })
}
export function useSetAgentState() {
  return useMutation({ mutationFn: ({ agentId, state }) => setAgentState(agentId, state) })
}

